com.xilinx.rapidwright.timing

Class TimingGraph

  • Object
    • <any>
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.timing.TimingGraph

  • public class TimingGraph
extends <any>
    A TimingGraph is an acyclic weighted-directed graph representing logic delays and physical net delays based on analyzing the circuits within Design objects.

        public float getDelay(<any> graphPath)
        Gets the delay/weight of a GraphPath
        Parameters:

        Returns:

      • setTimingRequirement

        public Float getWorstSlack()

      • getMaxDelayPath

        public <any> getMaxDelayPath()
        Finds and returns the path from the TimingGraph having maximum delay.
        Returns:
        The GraphPath that is the critical path found in the TimingGraph, which might be null if the GraphPaths haven't been pre-computed by calling TimingGraph.buildGraphPaths().

      • generateGraphvizDotVisualization

        public void generateGraphvizDotVisualization(String dotFileName)
        This creates a GraphViz library dot file representation of the TimingGraph. Might be useful for visualizing tiny designs. The resulting digraph() might be too large to render depending on the size of design.
        Parameters:
        dotFileName - The output filename for the writing the .dot file.

      • getGraphPaths

        public HashSet<<any>> getGraphPaths()
        Returns a set of built GraphPaths.
        Returns:
        The HashSet of current set of GraphPaths that were prebuilt by running buildGraphPaths()

      • buildGraphPaths

        public List<<any>> buildGraphPaths()
        Builds and returns a set of GraphPaths.
        Returns:
        A List of GraphPaths that were just built by this command

      • buildGraphPaths

        public List<<any>> buildGraphPaths(int n)
        Builds and returns a set of GraphPaths.
        Parameters:
        n - 0 will return all paths; 1 will return 1 path by using Bellman Ford algorithm with negating the edges prior to running the shortest path algorithm.
        Returns:
        A List of GraphPaths that were just built by this command
